text: Henry Newcombe (1835 - 26 October 1908) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1860/61 and 1862/63. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1835 births Category:1908 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Henry Newcombe (cricketer)
